        <li>Name of the device.</li>
        <li>Main language used by the user.</li>
        <li>Version of the operating system used.</li>
        <li>User active session by version.</li>
        <li>Active session per user.</li>
        <li>Number of active users.</li>
        <li>Error and crash report.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
        However, v38armageddon can choose software who not collect data at all, for example: Vincent OS, does not collect any data at all whether it is the normal version, the Linux version, or the Application version.
        <br />
        For more information, consult <a href="https://gist.github.com/v38armageddon">https://gist.github.com/v38armageddon</a> for more Privacy Policy for every software.
    </p>
    <br />
    <h3><strong>How do we collect your data?</strong></h3>
    <p>
        You directly provide v38armageddon with most of the data we collect. We collect data and process data when you:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Voluntarily complete a customer survey or provide feedback on any of our message boards or via email.</li>
