        <li>Use our software.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>v38armageddon may also receive your data indirectly from the following sources:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Visual Studio App Center</li>
        <li>Microsoft Partner Center</li>
    </ul>
    <br />
    <h3><strong>How will we use your data?</strong></h3>
    <p>v38armageddon collects your data so that we can:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Find the reason why the software doesn’t work. (Example: A software crash, we will use the crash report to find the reason why the software crashed and where the crash begins.)</li>
        <li>Analyze the data to improve the software. (Example: We will analyze the data to find the most used operating system of the software and improve its version.)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>v38armageddon does not share your data with partner companies.</p>
    <br />
